<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Johnny_Mathis&action=edit&section=9.php.html" title="Edit section: Million sellers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Million_sellers">Million sellers</span></h3>
<p>Mathis' million selling discs include the singles "Wonderful Wonderful", "It's Not For Me To Say", "Chances Are" (over two million), "Misty" (over two million), "When A Child Is Born" ( over 6 million worldwide ) and "Too Much, Too Little, Too Late" (over five million). His million selling albums include <i>Johnny's Greatest Hits</i> (approaching five million), <i>Merry Christmas</i> (approximately six million), <i>Heavenly</i> (over two million), <i>Give Me Your Love For Christmas</i>, <i>All Time Greatest Hits</i> (over two million) and <i>You Light Up My Life</i> (also over two million).</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Johnny_Mathis&action=edit&section=10.php.html" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Bibliography">Bibliography</span></h2>
